text = "To make a piece of [wave]text[/wave] bold enclose it in [b][/b], e.g.

[b]Hello[/b]

will become Hello
For underlining use [u][/u], for example:

[u]Good Morning[/u]

becomes Good Morning
To italicise text use [i][/i], e.g.

This is [i]Great![/i]

would give This is Great!"

